$Source: /home/cvsroot/ptk/INSTALL,v $

In this directory try

  cd src/ptk
  ln -s src/ptk/x11/* src/ptk/
  libtoolize
  aclocal
  automake --add-missing
  autoconf
  ./configure --disable-static
  gmake install

Libraries will be installed to /usr/local/lib, binaries to /usr/local/bin.
If libraries could not be found; add '/usr/local/lib' to /etc/ld.so.conf.
